A '''cargo floater''' was a [[Hoversled/Legends|repulsorsled]] which could carry large amounts of cargo. [[Wheel Security Force|Wheel Security]] employed such [[Droid/Legends|droids]] to transport stunned prisoners or [[Death/Legends|dead]] [[Gladiator/Legends|gladiators]].

